title: POLYGON Update: Collateral Factor, Collateral Cap, Asset Listings - Mass Update
body:
Intro: This is a vote to update the collateral factors and collateral caps on the POLYGON C.R.E.A.M. market AND add list new assets.

Proposal: Listing Committee

Rational: Update and improve POLYGON market.


For:
Update Collateral Factors and Collateral Caps EXACTLY as displayed in sheets (polygon tab) AND add 'new' assets to market — https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zZlTitPtIO-JMXDq_G19ScBpScbYE3q6WvXSHygykGY/edit#gid=1243313452

Against:
Do not make any changes to POLYGON market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
